review_blob:
Aroma: caramel, caramel, caramel, and something I cant identify but its not good.
Appearance: amber, clear, white foam, frothy, 
Taste: heavy cloying sweetness, lightly bitter, caramel
Palate: light body, thin feel, soft carbonation,

Aroma: citrus, spruce,
Appearance: pale, hazy
Taste: medium sweetness, medium bitterness, 
Palate: light body, lively, bitter,
Its not the best beer from this brewery, but its not really bad. I think that there should be more citrus aroma.
